### Get all events
GET {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Create event
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventName": "Saturday Night",
  "eventDate": "2026-02-21",
  "minDeposit": 20,
  "sectionPricing": {
    "A": 40,
    "B": 50,
    "C": 70,
    "D": 100,
    "E": 250
  },
  "disabledTables": ["A01", "A02"],
  "disabledClients": []
}

###

### Get event by date
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/by-date/2026-02-21
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Update event
@eventId = 1770508830523-dd669096-3adf-4a8f-9942-d5ac35eebfb5
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

###

### Reactivate event (will fail with 409 if another event exists for the date)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###

### Delete event
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
